sequenceDiagram
    %% RHOAI MCP Server - Data Flow Diagram
    %% Generated from: architecture/rhoai.next/rhoai-mcp.md

    participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude Desktop / LLM)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Edge
    participant MCP as RHOAI MCP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant NeuralNav as Neural Navigator<br/>8000/TCP HTTP In-Cluster
    participant PortFwd as Port Forward<br/>(oc port-forward)
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP In-Cluster
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Agent,S3: Flow 1: Standard K8s Resource Operations (e.g. deploy model, create workbench)

    Agent->>Route: POST /mcp (MCP tool call)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3
    Route->>MCP: Forward (TLS edge termination)<br/>HTTP/8000
    MCP->>MCP: Plugin Manager routes<br/>to domain plugin
    MCP->>K8s: Create/Get/List/Update/Delete resource<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token (SA/kubeconfig)
    K8s-->>MCP: Resource response<br/>HTTPS/6443
    MCP->>MCP: ResponseBuilder formats<br/>(verbosity: minimal/standard/full)
    MCP-->>Route: MCP tool result<br/>HTTP/8000
    Route-->>Agent: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Agent,S3: Flow 2: Model Recommendation via Neural Navigator

    Agent->>MCP: recommend_model tool call<br/>(stdio or HTTP)
    MCP->>NeuralNav: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP/8000, No Auth
    NeuralNav-->>MCP: Extracted intent
    MCP->>NeuralNav: POST /api/v1/ranked-recommend-from-spec<br/>HTTP/8000, No Auth
    NeuralNav-->>MCP: Ranked model recommendations
    MCP-->>Agent: Recommendation results

    Agent->>MCP: get_deployment_config tool call
    MCP->>NeuralNav: POST /api/v1/deploy<br/>HTTP/8000, No Auth
    NeuralNav-->>MCP: K8s YAML (InferenceService, HPA, ServiceMonitor)
    MCP-->>Agent: Ready-to-apply deployment configs

    Note over Agent,S3: Flow 3: Model Registry Query with Port-Forward

    Agent->>MCP: list_registered_models tool call<br/>(stdio or HTTP)
    MCP->>MCP: Discover ModelRegistry CRs<br/>& Route endpoints
    MCP->>PortFwd: Start oc port-forward<br/>to Model Registry pod
    PortFwd->>ModelReg: TCP tunnel established<br/>local:dynamic → 8080/TCP
    MCP->>ModelReg: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTP/8080, None/OAuth/Bearer
    ModelReg-->>MCP: Model metadata response
    MCP-->>Agent: Formatted model list

    Note over Agent,S3: Flow 4: Data Connection Validation

    Agent->>MCP: create_s3_data_connection tool call
    MCP->>K8s: Create Secret (S3 credentials)<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8s-->>MCP: Secret created
    MCP->>S3: Validate S3 endpoint connectivity<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>MCP: Connection validated
    MCP-->>Agent: Data connection created & validated
